<lyrics>[V1]
 lái ba ràng wǒ men yǒng yuè zàn měi jiāng róng yào guī gěi tā
 lái ba ràng wǒ men yǒng yuè zàn měi jiāng róng yào guī gěi tā
 de shàng de wàn mín hé jūn wáng dōu lái jìng bài tā
 zhàn zài shén diàn zhōng de yě yào yī xīn chēng xiè tā
 tā shì shēng mìng de yuán tóu ài de yuán tóu
 tā de zuò wèi hé dà néng yǐ chuán biàn tiān xià
 tā ràng wǒ men jǐn jǐn lián jiē bǐ cǐ xiāng ài
 lái ba ràng wǒ men yǒng yuè zàn měi jiāng róng yào guī gěi tā</lyrics>
